name: RockPaperScissor
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: rock paper scissor
des:
User has to select one among rock, paper and scissor. The skill in its backend will randomly select any one of rock, paper or scissor.
Then using the game logic, winner will be decided.
User can win the game or lose the game or a tie can occur.
The user also access to scoreboard which keeps track of wins,losses and ties.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
